title: Amazon's grocery service now requires a $299 yearly membership
text:
Amazon's grocery service now requires a $299 yearly membership 
Published By: Tuaw.com - Today 
Amazon warned late last year that it would eventually require a $299 yearly membership just to use its AmazonFresh grocery delivery service....
